Photosensitive light sensor
  VCC ---> +3.3V
  GND ---> GND 6
  AO ---> ADC 0

Ultrasonic Distance Sensor
  VCC ---> +3.3V
  Trig ---> GPIO 23
  Echo ---> GPIO 24
  GND ---> GND 30

Sound Sensor
  VCC ---> +3.3V
  GND ---> GND 20
  OUT ---> GPIO 17

  OUT ---> ADC 1

ADC MCP3008
  VDD ---> +3.3V
  VREF ---> +3.3V
  AGND ---> GND (-3.3V)
  CLK ---> SCLK
  DOUT ---> MISO
  DIN ---> MOSI
  CS/SHDN ---> CEO
  DGND ---> GND (-3.3V)

LED
  Anode ---> 18
  Cathode ---> Resistor
  Resistor ---> GND


